name: W-BASE: Killing It
description:
The W-Base "Durcus 1" frames are known as one of the cleverest trick frames on the market. The Guys from W-base put all their BMX-knowledge into their frames and so far we did not hear from one frame that break - incredible. W-Base frames let the tubes work and do not use gussets that cause stresspoints and bring the risk to break. At the same time the W-Base frames seem to be the lightest of all trickframes.


The "Killing It" frame is 26", pure trick and for bombing parks or streets.

Specs:
  • Seat tube: 410mm
  • Chainstay: 403,5mm
  • Head angle: 74°

  • Bottom bracket: spanish (73mm wide) / negative -10°
  • Rear dropout: 14mm (incl. chain tensioner)
